{"tid":26942,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"R quantmod 討論","createTime":"2016-12-07T04:27:28.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T08:14:58.000Z","uid":58109,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e0ab9e0fa89e3c13a02c0cb8992310cd70d729a6","tid":26942,"uid":58109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T04:27:29.000Z","msg":"初學R，用左佢黎做backtest，<br />\n<br />\n只做call，<br />\n每次做一單，<br />\n要放左貨先可以做下一單，<br />\n止蝕-120點，<br />\n由2007開始到宜家賺15000點左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我見有d可以做到幾萬點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔知點做到<br />\n有無巴士打以分享下你地做到幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://holland.pk/6rq8u1i4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6rq8u1i4&h=ed68181c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"69881680a2c0b38f43d6708b5aa905419c1b03ac","tid":26942,"uid":57886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:01:04.000Z","msg":"你用daily data ?"},{"pid":"f3ae9a36e4bb523f86f57fdc64042699301809a8","tid":26942,"uid":31513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:29:44.000Z","msg":"我學緊R 有冇啲咩書/文可以推薦下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7906daecaee79dc69c44c340c660ecdb0fc550a","tid":26942,"uid":58109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:06:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我學緊R 有冇啲咩書/文可以推薦下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係上網學, 無咩書...<br />\n我覺得呢個網幾好, STEP BY STEP教你, 又有PRATICE做<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.datacamp.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.datacamp.com%2F&d=UvprCxjRFPMsPvJ3PrIHF3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=f437381a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.datacamp.com/</a>"},{"pid":"6b8d561336c9c35b446ffa47b29c583a6db66e49","tid":26942,"uid":58109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:08:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你用daily data ?</blockquote><br />\n無錯, 巴打都有研究開???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d322c8c2361e7f7eb5daad85fbed83c71366816c","tid":26942,"uid":34892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:09:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>初學R，用左佢黎做backtest，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只做call，<br />\n<br />\n每次做一單，<br />\n<br />\n要放左貨先可以做下一單，<br />\n<br />\n止蝕-120點，<br />\n<br />\n由2007開始到宜家賺15000點左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我見有d可以做到幾萬點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都唔知點做到<br />\n<br />\n有無巴士打以分享下你地做到幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://holland.pk/6rq8u1i4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6rq8u1i4&h=ed68181c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n點做backtest?<br />\n利申:剩係識R"},{"pid":"fec26cfd70c08fbc354589c2d80b0acb53adb60a","tid":26942,"uid":58109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T09:29:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>初學R，用左佢黎做backtest，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只做call，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每次做一單，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要放左貨先可以做下一單，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n止蝕-120點，<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由2007開始到宜家賺15000點左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我見有d可以做到幾萬點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都唔知點做到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有無巴士打以分享下你地做到幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://holland.pk/6rq8u1i4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6rq8u1i4&h=ed68181c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點做backtest?<br />\n<br />\n利申:剩係識R</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己諗D RULES, 之後再用 R 寫番出黎, 我都係初學, 比想像中簡單,<br />\nExample: <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bituzi.com/2014/12/Rbacktest6mins.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bituzi.com%2F2014%2F12%2FRbacktest6mins.html&d=UvprCxjRFPMsPvJ3PrIHF3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=2ef8c30c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bituzi.com/2014/12/Rbacktest6mins.html</a>"},{"pid":"2be399bc0282c6bed5613c7b4264e1792060c388","tid":26942,"uid":57886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:35:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你用daily data ?</blockquote><br />\n無錯, 巴打都有研究開???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n用R做 portfolio 多<br />\nAlgo 用python"},{"pid":"e87c992a67ea1c4120dfc44c433ac461a8c911a8","tid":26942,"uid":57549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T10:50:35.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"a95251235ef305e7bdc0f200a17525904fc2d4ed","tid":26942,"uid":58109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:31:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你用daily data ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯, 巴打都有研究開???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用R做 portfolio 多<br />\n<br />\nAlgo 用python</blockquote><br />\n有無試過做HSI portfolio幾多??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58dd5f47608fb5c1faff8235d1b80979c325e76b","tid":26942,"uid":56690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T11:33:42.000Z","msg":"巴打有冇計埋每一單交易既滑價同埋佣金？<br />\n<br />\n同埋有冇多啲backtest 既statistic 參考下<br />\n例如：win rate , average P/L ratio , MDD<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b627d554bb3267c35de4ca82bb10061a0f3f98b7","tid":26942,"uid":58109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T12:02:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打有冇計埋每一單交易既滑價同埋佣金？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋有冇多啲backtest 既statistic 參考下<br />\n<br />\n例如：win rate , average P/L ratio , MDD<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無計到佣金,當用一通, 同埋唔識咩叫滑價<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\naverage P/L ratio 即係所有盈利加埋再除交易次數??<br />\nMDD 唔知咩黎..<br />\n新手求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"becba336219c1b78343768d7db6bfb7b44d75d57","tid":26942,"uid":51673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:10:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同技術分析有咩分別?"},{"pid":"6aab47363df648b5ffc4e22f94515187bce82789","tid":26942,"uid":53262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:32:12.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"1c15d4e75d8f84e723c215c913fa09b8bb09757a","tid":26942,"uid":44460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T13:45:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打有冇計埋每一單交易既滑價同埋佣金？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋有冇多啲backtest 既statistic 參考下<br />\n<br />\n例如：win rate , average P/L ratio , MDD<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無計到佣金,當用一通, 同埋唔識咩叫滑價<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\naverage P/L ratio 即係所有盈利加埋再除交易次數??<br />\nMDD 唔知咩黎..<br />\n新手求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n實戰最好計埋手續費, 你target 嗰格同你食糊嗰格個variance / correlation.<br />\n其他R有 function call."},{"pid":"475466d6997e9969c5f63f4ca87686e27e126b5d","tid":26942,"uid":57886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:09:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你用daily data ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無錯, 巴打都有研究開???<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n用R做 portfolio 多<br />\n<br />\nAlgo 用python</blockquote><br />\n有無試過做HSI portfolio幾多??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做過標普細期，好廢，2016 除佣後賺68點<br />\n遲下會試埋HSFI"},{"pid":"4f27291d17f097a64a124c80927db2360d6b47be","tid":26942,"uid":45898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T16:19:00.000Z","msg":"丁下留名"},{"pid":"552091c037addca64e7e1bf0be683a3bad19b6e0","tid":26942,"uid":56690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T10:52:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打有冇計埋每一單交易既滑價同埋佣金？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋有冇多啲backtest 既statistic 參考下<br />\n<br />\n例如：win rate , average P/L ratio , MDD<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無計到佣金,當用一通, 同埋唔識咩叫滑價<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\naverage P/L ratio 即係所有盈利加埋再除交易次數??<br />\nMDD 唔知咩黎..<br />\n新手求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為用到algo做trade<br />\n我假設用IB做trade細期<br />\n一張細期佣金$17來回就$34<br />\n另外因為有bid ask spread 同埋time delay<br />\n你保守預2點來回4點滑價 (即係$40)<br />\n<br />\n所以backtest果陣每一個來回trade都要減返$74<br />\n先會比較貼近實戰情況<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nProfit/Loss Ratio <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.investopedia.com/inv/dictionary/terms/Profitlossnew.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.investopedia.com%2Finv%2Fdictionary%2Fterms%2FProfitlossnew.gif&h=ac41391a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMDD<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.investopedia.com/terms/m/maximum-drawdown-mdd.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.investopedia.com%2Fterms%2Fm%2Fmaximum-drawdown-mdd.asp&d=UvprCxjRFPMsPvJ3PrIHF3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=23ae6330\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.investopedia.com/terms/m/maximum-drawdown-mdd.asp</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307a01b93ac1c50a534e849cff4db5f7b9bc8955","tid":26942,"uid":58109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T14:35:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打有冇計埋每一單交易既滑價同埋佣金？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋有冇多啲backtest 既statistic 參考下<br />\n<br />\n例如：win rate , average P/L ratio , MDD<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無計到佣金,當用一通, 同埋唔識咩叫滑價<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\naverage P/L ratio 即係所有盈利加埋再除交易次數??<br />\nMDD 唔知咩黎..<br />\n新手求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為用到algo做trade<br />\n我假設用IB做trade細期<br />\n一張細期佣金$17來回就$34<br />\n另外因為有bid ask spread 同埋time delay<br />\n你保守預2點來回4點滑價 (即係$40)<br />\n<br />\n所以backtest果陣每一個來回trade都要減返$74<br />\n先會比較貼近實戰情況<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nProfit/Loss Ratio <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.investopedia.com/inv/dictionary/terms/Profitlossnew.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.investopedia.com%2Finv%2Fdictionary%2Fterms%2FProfitlossnew.gif&h=ac41391a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMDD<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.investopedia.com/terms/m/maximum-drawdown-mdd.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.investopedia.com%2Fterms%2Fm%2Fmaximum-drawdown-mdd.asp&d=UvprCxjRFPMsPvJ3PrIHF3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=23ae6330\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.investopedia.com/terms/m/maximum-drawdown-mdd.asp</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱啱再調過，用今年HSI數據<br />\n超過-50點就止蝕，佣金＋滑價出入我當成本用左8點<br />\n<br />\n成年總共賺1629點，<br />\n<br />\nTotal Gain = 3756,<br />\nnumber of winning trades = 5<br />\nTotal Loss = -2127<br />\nnumber of Losing Trades = 10<br />\n<br />\nProfit/Loss Ratio = 3.53<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諗住用charts.PerformanceSummary 呢個FUNCTION，<br />\n點知Error in na.omit.xts(x) : unsupported type<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a4146c7d16c2e9dcd30be0727fc2779fe5ead6","tid":26942,"uid":56690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T18:36:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴打有冇計埋每一單交易既滑價同埋佣金？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋有冇多啲backtest 既statistic 參考下<br />\n<br />\n例如：win rate , average P/L ratio , MDD<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無計到佣金,當用一通, 同埋唔識咩叫滑價<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\naverage P/L ratio 即係所有盈利加埋再除交易次數??<br />\nMDD 唔知咩黎..<br />\n新手求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為用到algo做trade<br />\n我假設用IB做trade細期<br />\n一張細期佣金$17來回就$34<br />\n另外因為有bid ask spread 同埋time delay<br />\n你保守預2點來回4點滑價 (即係$40)<br />\n<br />\n所以backtest果陣每一個來回trade都要減返$74<br />\n先會比較貼近實戰情況<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nProfit/Loss Ratio <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.investopedia.com/inv/dictionary/terms/Profitlossnew.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.investopedia.com%2Finv%2Fdictionary%2Fterms%2FProfitlossnew.gif&h=ac41391a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nMDD<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.investopedia.com/terms/m/maximum-drawdown-mdd.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.investopedia.com%2Fterms%2Fm%2Fmaximum-drawdown-mdd.asp&d=UvprCxjRFPMsPvJ3PrIHF3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=23ae6330\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.investopedia.com/terms/m/maximum-drawdown-mdd.asp</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱啱再調過，用今年HSI數據<br />\n超過-50點就止蝕，佣金＋滑價出入我當成本用左8點<br />\n<br />\n成年總共賺1629點，<br />\n<br />\nTotal Gain = 375